          <p class="first-para" id="S5LV0664P0-10704">Listed below are the names of special advisers in post at 19 July 2004, the special advisers' pay ranges for 2004&#x2013;05, the number of special advisers in each pay band by department and the total cost of special advisers for 2003&#x2013;04.</p><p id="S5LV0664P0-10705">All special advisers are appointed under terms and conditions set out in the Model Contract for Special Advisers providing advice on the full range of their appointing Minister's departmental responsibilities. Where a special adviser has a specific expertise this is indicated.</p><a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_41ws' title='Col. 41WS &mdash; HL Deb 22 July 2004 vol 664 c41WS' name='column_41ws' href='#column_41ws' rel='bookmark'>41WS</a><p id="S5LV0664P0-10706">
