          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td><sup>4</sup>Plus Sue Nye appointed as an unpaid adviser.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td><sup>5</sup>Plus two special advisers who are paid beyond pay band 4, but within the scheme maximum.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td><sup>6</sup>Plus one adviser who is unpaid.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td><sup>7</sup>Plus the five members of the Council of Economic Advisers who are employed on special adviser terms (one in band 4, three in band 3 and one in band 1). One of the members of the council works part-time.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td><sup>8</sup>This figure includes salary, severance pay and an estimate of pensions cost.</td>
          </tr>
